snippet.title: Dungeonland Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy the game: http://www.dungeonlandgame.com/buy
http://www.facebook.com/Dungeonland
https://twitter.com/dungeonland


Paradox Interactive, a publisher of games and consumer of funnel cake, today announced that Dungeonland will opened its doors to easily lured heroes everywhere. Available today for PC via digital distributors worldwide, Dungeonland can be purchased, downloaded, played, and quickly lost over and over again by soft, fleshy adventurers to their heart's content. Dungeonland costs merely $9.99 plus the lives of your co-op partners.
